OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA windy
OL,6,Fevening with gales along the east
OL,7,Fcoast. Outbreaks of rain turning
OL,8,Fheavier in south and east but little
OL,9,Freaching the north coast. Clearer
OL,10,Fovernight then showers in west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FBright or sunny intervals
OL,13,Fand showers, frequent in the west at
OL,14,Ffirst. Strong to gale westerly winds
OL,15,Fslowly easing.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,18,Frain on Thursday then sunny intervals
OL,19,Fand blustery showers, Colder Friday
OL,20,Fwith showers wintry at first. Saturday
OL,21,Fbright and breezy with a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
